{"tid":99810,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"真心有個會睇波既親戚真係好幸福","createTime":"2017-01-29T13:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T14:33:17.000Z","uid":9428,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c0c6d9ab93ccaed303a50ffc21c0ca7ec4d7f2d7","tid":99810,"uid":9428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:11:18.000Z","msg":"好簡單<br />\n<br />\n唔怕無話題，<span style=\"color: red;\">講下轉會窗同比賽</span>又捱過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家拜年最驚都係問三問四又無得駁，有睇波又唔同講法，<span style=\"color: red;\">轉下話題抽下佢撐個隊波水</span>，受氣之餘起碼有得還拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗四字祝福語好難？ 有睇波又唔同講法，簡單一句<span style=\"color: red;\">英超冠軍</span>，拍拍心口又一條好漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：親戚係利迷"},{"pid":"0c4e2ddb562310746122258bd39b160c90096ba7","tid":99810,"uid":17522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:12:48.000Z","msg":"紅字有咩意思？"},{"pid":"cb034c185c23319a6aeed0f8fe171db29fe63fd5","tid":99810,"uid":9428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:20:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>紅字有咩意思？</blockquote><br />\n重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d4ca6019ddbec92db72a2b69e05c1bbf4924444","tid":99810,"uid":9428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:06:33.000Z","msg":"邊個利迷留下負皮"},{"pid":"d7907ea1e71af8526526297581d2991b713ee9d2","tid":99810,"uid":38144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:08:12.000Z","msg":"正一足球毒撚 淨係識講波？"},{"pid":"60d0ab5c0fb069539330604da59dd3ccb66be315","tid":99810,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:31:29.000Z","msg":"不了 一個係曼狗一個利狗咪赤口"},{"pid":"21d021152cbb6dac174e75a6e52700b52ccf55cc","tid":99810,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0